---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Portugal Car Rental Guide | TripAxle"
  description="A practical Portugal car rental guide for English-speaking travelers."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Portugal car rental guide</p>
    <h1>Renting a car in Portugal: what to know before you book.</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      Start here if you want a practical overview of booking sites, airport
      pickups, insurance concerns, toll roads, and common rental mistakes in
      Portugal.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-grid">
    <article class="main-card">
      <h2>What this guide will help you do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Choose the best type of booking platform for your trip</li>
        <li>Understand airport pickup differences</li>
        <li>Avoid common insurance and toll misunderstandings</li>
        <li>Know what to double-check before you reserve</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Best place to start</h2>
      <p>
        If you already know your airport, the airport guides
        will be the fastest path.
      </p>
    </article>

    <aside class="side-card">
      <h2>Planned Portugal sections</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Lisbon Airport car rental</li>
        <li>Porto Airport car rental</li>
        <li>Faro Airport car rental</li>
        <li>Insurance guide</li>
        <li>Toll roads guide</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <style>
    .hero {
      padding: 2rem 0 2.25rem;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      color: #2f6fed;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      line-height: 1.08;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      color: #5b5b55;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 680px;
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .main-card,
    .side-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e4e4de;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
    }

    li + li {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .content-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>